data.description: Welcome Home! Well maintained single family home featuring an open and spacious concept. A grand 2- story foyer welcomes you as you enter the front door and make your way upstairs to the large great room with vaulted ceilings. Kitchen opens up to the dining area and the living room. Spacious owner's suite features en suite with a separate tub and shower plus there's a large walk in closet. On the garage level you will find an additional full bathroom and 2 additional bedrooms. Spacious deck right off the kitchen backdoor perfect for entertaining, relaxing and looking out onto the large private backyard. 2 car garage with ample storage. Great location, move in ready, schedule your tour today.
